column2: "There...? Or is it there? ...Why can't this body sense it?!"
"The place where my power was broken before, it should be here!"
"Why can't I detect my own power...?!"
"...You seem upset, Dark Falz. No... Yuki-nee."
"Tsk! ARKS...! Stop calling me that disgusting name!"
"...I won't stop, I'll call you that as many times as it takes for you to remember!"
"Please calm down. Your voice is reaching her."

"It's different from the me that was chasing ghosts. If you keep at it,
you'll surely get through to her."
"Partner... Heh, that's right! It's still too early to give in!"
"Alright, let's get through these guys and find Yuki-nee again!"
